subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Drag Races
content:
Climb gears and leave opponents in the rearview by exerting maximum control over your vehicle in Drag Races.

Launch Drag Races from the comfort of your iFruit or visit the LS Car Meet and hit the Nitrous for 2X GTA$ and RP this week.
